TY  - JOUR
T1  - Sugar Cane Irrigation: A Case Study in Capital Budgeting
AU  - Champion, Robert R.
AU  - Glaser, R. George
Y1  - 1967/08/01
PY  - 1967
DA  - 1967/08/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.13.12.B781
